{
  "dataSources": [
    {
      "ID": "plugin-runs",
      "fields": [
        { "name": "id",         "type": "integer", "primaryKey": true },
        { "name": "pluginId",   "type": "text" },
        { "name": "flowName",   "type": "text" },
        { "name": "ts",         "type": "integer" },
        { "name": "durationMs", "type": "integer" },
        { "name": "success",    "type": "boolean" },
        { "name": "error",      "type": "text" },
        { "name": "sharedIn",   "type": "text" },
        { "name": "sharedOut",  "type": "text" }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "layout": {
    "_type": "VLayout",
    "ID": "pfResumeParserRoot",
    "width": "100%",
    "height": "100%",
    "overflow": "auto",
    "padding": 16,
    "membersMargin": 12,
    "members": [
      {
        "_type": "Label",
        "height": 28,
        "contents": "<div style='font-size:18px;font-weight:600;color:#a8b4ff;'>Resume Parser (PocketFlow)</div>"
      },
      {
        "_type": "Label",
        "height": 50,
        "contents": "<div style='font-size:12px;color:#888;line-height:1.5;'>Single-Node PocketFlow flow with retries. Calls the bridge's <code>/llm</code> endpoint with a strict JSON schema; the LLM returns parsed structured fields. The <b>prompt template is editable below</b> — change the wording and re-run to see how it affects extraction. Markers <code>{resume}</code> and <code>{skills}</code> get substituted at run time.</div>"
      },
      {
        "_type": "DynamicForm",
        "ID": "parseForm",
        "width": "100%",
        "height": 600,
        "numCols": 2,
        "colWidths": [80, "*"],
        "fields": [
          {
            "name": "resume_text",
            "title": "Resume",
            "type": "textArea",
            "height": 200,
            "width": "*",
            "defaultValue": "# JOHN SMTIH\n\n**Email:** johnsmtih1983@gnail.com\n**Phone:** (555) 123-4556\n\n## WORK EXPERIENCE\n\n### SALES MANAGER\n**ABC Corporation** | June 2018 - Present\n- Oversee a team of 12 sales representatives\n- Implemented new CRM system that improved efficiency by 15%\n- Collaborate with Marketing team on campaigns\n\n### ASSISTANT MANAGER\n**XYZ Industries** | March 2015 - May 2018\n- Managed inventory and vendor relations\n- Trained junior staff using Microsoft Office tools\n\n## EDUCATION\n**Bachelor of Business Administration** | University of Somewhere | 2010"
          },
          {
            "name": "target_skills",
            "title": "Skills",
            "type": "textArea",
            "height": 60,
            "width": "*",
            "defaultValue": "Team leadership, CRM software, Project management, Public speaking, Microsoft Office, Python, Data Analysis"
          },
          {
            "name": "prompt_template",
            "title": "Prompt",
            "type": "textArea",
            "height": 280,
            "width": "*",
            "defaultValue": "Extract structured fields from the resume below.\n\n**Resume:**\n```\n{resume}\n```\n\n**Target Skills (use these indexes):**\n```\n{skills}\n```\n\nReturn:\n- name (string): full name extracted from the resume\n- email (string): email address\n- experience: array of {title, company} objects, one per job\n- skill_indexes: array of integer indexes into the target skills list, one per skill found in the resume"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "Label",
        "height": 36,
        "contents": "<div style='font-size:11px;color:#888;line-height:1.4;'><b>Skills:</b> comma-separated list of target skills the parser will look for. <b>Prompt:</b> editable template — markers <code>{resume}</code> and <code>{skills}</code> are substituted at run time.</div>"
      },
      {
        "_type": "HLayout",
        "height": 36,
        "membersMargin": 8,
        "members": [
          {
            "_type": "Button",
            "ID": "btnParse",
            "title": "Parse Resume",
            "width": 200,
            "_action": "dispatchAndDisplay",
            "_messageType": "PF_RESUME_PARSE",
            "_payloadFrom": "parseForm",
            "_targetCanvas": "outputParsed",
            "_resultPath": "parsed",
            "_resultFormatter": "json",
            "_timeoutMs": 90000
          },
          {
            "_type": "Button",
            "ID": "btnShared",
            "title": "Show full state",
            "width": 200,
            "_action": "dispatchAndDisplay",
            "_messageType": "PF_RESUME_PARSE",
            "_payloadFrom": "parseForm",
            "_targetCanvas": "outputShared",
            "_resultFormatter": "json",
            "_timeoutMs": 90000
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "Label",
        "height": 18,
        "contents": "<div style='font-size:11px;color:#666;'>Parsed fields (extracted via <code>_resultPath: \"parsed\"</code>)</div>"
      },
      {
        "_type": "HTMLFlow",
        "ID": "outputParsed",
        "height": 220,
        "padding": 4,
        "overflow": "auto",
        "contents": "<em style='color:#888;'>Click \"Parse Resume\" to extract structured fields.</em>"
      },
      {
        "_type": "Label",
        "height": 18,
        "contents": "<div style='font-size:11px;color:#666;'>Full shared state (after the flow runs)</div>"
      },
      {
        "_type": "HTMLFlow",
        "ID": "outputShared",
        "height": 200,
        "padding": 4,
        "overflow": "auto",
        "contents": "<em style='color:#888;'>Click \"Show full state\" for the complete response.</em>"
      },
      {
        "_type": "Label",
        "height": 22,
        "contents": "<div style='font-size:12px;color:#aaa;font-weight:600;margin-top:8px;'>Run history</div>"
      },
      {
        "_type": "HLayout",
        "height": 28,
        "membersMargin": 8,
        "members": [
          {
            "_type": "Button",
            "ID": "btnRefreshHistory",
            "title": "Refresh",
            "width": 100,
            "_action": "dsFetch",
            "_targetGrid": "runHistoryGrid"
          },
          {
            "_type": "Label",
            "height": 24,
            "width": "*",
            "contents": "<div style='font-size:11px;color:#888;'>Every Parse run is recorded in IndexedDB (<code>plugin-runs</code> store). Click a row to inspect the run.</div>"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "ListGrid",
        "ID": "runHistoryGrid",
        "height": 220,
        "dataSource": "plugin-runs",
        "autoFetchData": true,
        "initialCriteria": { "pluginId": "pf-resume-parser" },
        "sortField": "ts",
        "sortDirection": "descending",
        "showHeader": true,
        "canEdit": false,
        "emptyMessage": "No runs yet — click Parse to record one.",
        "fields": [
          { "name": "ts",         "title": "When",       "width": 160, "_formatter": "timestamp" },
          { "name": "durationMs", "title": "Duration",   "width": 90,  "align": "right" },
          { "name": "success",    "title": "OK",         "width": 50,  "type": "boolean" },
          { "name": "flowName",   "title": "Flow",       "width": 140 },
          { "name": "error",      "title": "Error",      "width": "*"  }
        ]
      }
    ]
  }
}
